00:40:38.000 --> 00:40:38.670
Vamos entonces.

00:40:39.190 --> 00:40:41.040
No hay problema.

00:40:51.670 --> 00:40:52.360
Xiaoyuan,

00:40:53.070 --> 00:40:54.270
